actions.message:
List of commands
```
Everyone -
<help - Lists available commands.
<coinflip - Flips a coin
<ping [@user] - Pings a staff for help

Moderator -
<kick [@user] [reason] - Kicks the mentioned user.
<ban [@user] [reason] - Bans the mentioned user.
<warn [@user] [reason] - Warns the mentioned user.
<mute [@user] - Mutes the user in voice chat
<unmute [@user] - Unmutes the user in voice chat

Administrator -
<delete-channel [#channel] - Deletes the mentioned channel.
<delete-role [#channel] - Deletes the mentioned role.
```
